      ],
      "start": 11.85,
      "text": "Good morning. Weather data is unavailable right now; we start with the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a3b1fba2b36"
      ],
      "end": 33.03,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 16.41,
      "text": "Google DeepMind has released DiffusionGemma, an experimental open model designed for exceptionally fast text generation. NVIDIA has already optimized the model to increase speeds across GeForce RTX GPUs and the RTX PRO platform."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "adc9faf6384"
      ],
      "end": 52.58,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s4",
        "s5",
        "s6"
      ],
      "start": 34.07,
      "text": "While technical infrastructure advances, political barriers in Europe are shifting. Hungary's new prime minister, Peter Magyar, has announced a historic minority rights deal with Ukraine. This agreement clears the path for Ukraine to begin EU accession negotiations after years of tension."
    },
    {
      "end": 56.28,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 52.86,
      "text": "Weather data remains unavailable for the closing update."
    },
    {
      "end": 59.94,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 56.68,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 61.296,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 59.94,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 63.5,
      "id": "p6",
